Package net.sodacan.module.variable

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Variable
    Interface to access one existing variable.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ClockVariable  
    ConfigVariable
    Provide access to selected configuration settings
    Constraint
    Constraint of a variable.
    IdentifierConstraint
    An identifier constraint in Sodacan is just a string (without quotes) The only challenge is that these pseudo-string must not conflict with other identifiers.
    ModuleVariable  
    NumberConstraint
    A number-constraint has constraints: A decimal number has a specific precision, such as 0.00, means the precision of a decimal number is 2.
    RangeConstraint  
    ShortcutVariable
    A Shortcut variable is like any other variable except that it also contains a condition as well.
    StringConstraint  
    SubscribeVariable
    A subscribe variable is just like any normal module variable except that it has additional attributes available that access the underlying message that populates the variable.
    VariableDef
    A Single Variable.
    VariableDef.VariableDefBuilder  
    VariableDefs
    A structure holding all variables for a module
